entry.def: A rota is a list which gives details of the order in which different people have to do a particular job.

example.ex: I suggest that you work out a careful rota which will make it clear who tidies the room on which day.
example.tran: 我建议你制定一个详细的值班表，明确哪一天由谁整理房间。
